        <mxCell id="diOuJLZaJ-emEz8I7TLT-246" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="Design a YouTube-like Video Sharing Platform with the following services:&#xa;&#xa;User Login Service&#xa;Video Upload Service&#xa;Video Streaming Service&#xa;Recommendation Service&#xa;Comment &amp; Engagement Service&#xa;&#xa;Implement a mechanism to detect and restrict copyrighted or policy-violating content uploads.&#xa;Optimize the personalized video recommendation feed for millions of users.&#xa;Highlight where a Back-Fill service can be used in the architecture." vertex="1">
